---
layout: layouts/base.njk
title: "Visa Sponsored Tech Jobs in the Netherlands | Software Engineering & More"
description: "Find visa-sponsored tech jobs in the Netherlands with relocation assistance. Browse software engineering, data science, and DevOps roles in Amsterdam, Rotterdam, Eindhoven and more."
permalink: /jobs-in-netherlands/
---

{% set country_name = "Netherlands" %}
{% set country_flag = "🇳🇱" %}
{% set grouped = jobs | groupByCountry %}
{% set countryJobs = grouped["Netherlands"] or [] %}

{% block structuredData %}
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "BreadcrumbList",
  "itemListElement": [
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 1, "name": "Home", "item": "{{ site.url }}/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 2, "name": "Jobs by Country", "item": "{{ site.url }}/jobs-by-country/" },
    { "@type": "ListItem", "position": 3, "name": "Netherlands", "item": "{{ site.url }}/jobs-in-netherlands/" }
  ]
}
</script>
<script type="application/ld+json">
{
  "@context": "https://schema.org",
  "@type": "CollectionPage",
  "name": "Visa Sponsored Tech Jobs in the Netherlands",
  "description": "Find {{ countryJobs | length }}+ visa-sponsored tech jobs in the Netherlands with relocation assistance.",
  "url": "{{ site.url }}/jobs-in-netherlands/",
  "publisher": { "@type": "Organization", "name": "{{ site.name }}", "url": "{{ site.url }}" },
  "mainEntity": {
    "@type": "ItemList",
    "numberOfItems": {{ countryJobs | length }},
    "itemListElement": [
      {% for job in countryJobs | limit(10) %}
      {
        "@type": "ListItem",
        "position": {{ loop.index }},
        "item": {
          "@type": "JobPosting",
          "title": "{{ job.position }}",
          "datePosted": "{{ job.post_date }}",
          "validThrough": "{{ job.post_date | validThrough }}",
          "description": "{{ job.position }} at {{ job.company }} in {{ job.location }}. Visa sponsorship and relocation assistance included.",
          "employmentType": "FULL_TIME",
          "hiringOrganization": {
            "@type": "Organization",
            "name": "{{ job.company }}",
            "logo": "{{ site.url }}{{ job.logo }}"
          },
          "jobLocation": {
            "@type": "Place",
            "address": {
              "@type": "PostalAddress",
              "streetAddress": "",
              "addressLocality": "{{ job.location | extractCity }}",
              "addressRegion": "{{ job.location | extractCity }}",
              "postalCode": "",
              "addressCountry": "NL"
            }
          },
          "url": "{{ job.description }}"
        }
      }{% if not loop.last %},{% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    ]
  }
}
</script>
{% endblock %}

{# Hero #}
<section class="bg-gradient-to-b from-brand-50 to-white dark:from-gray-900 dark:to-gray-950 py-12 md:py-16">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
    <nav class="flex items-center gap-2 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-6">
      <a href="/" class="hover:text-brand-600 dark:hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">Home</a>
      <i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
      <a href="/jobs-by-country/" class="hover:text-brand-600 dark:hover:text-brand-400 transition-colors">Jobs by Country</a>
      <i data-lucide="chevron-right" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
      <span class="text-gray-900 dark:text-white font-medium">Netherlands</span>
    </nav>
    <div class="flex items-center gap-4 mb-4">
      <span class="text-5xl">{{ country_flag }}</span>
      <div>
        <h1 class="text-3xl md:text-4xl font-extrabold text-gray-900 dark:text-white tracking-tight">
          Tech Jobs in the Netherlands
        </h1>
        <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mt-1">
          {{ countryJobs | length }} visa-sponsored positions with relocation assistance
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-3 mt-6">
      <span class="badge badge-visa">Visa Sponsorship</span>
      <span class="badge badge-reloc">Relocation Assistance</span>
      <span class="inline-flex items-center gap-1.5 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">
        <i data-lucide="map-pin" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
        Amsterdam, Rotterdam, Eindhoven & more
      </span>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# Job Listings #}
<section class="py-12">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4">
    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-6">
      <h2 class="section-heading">All Positions</h2>
      <span class="text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400">{{ countryJobs | length }} jobs</span>
    </div>

    <div class="space-y-4">
      {% for job in jobs %}
      {% if "Netherlands" in job.location %}
      <div class="job-card">
        <div class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row sm:items-start gap-4">
          <img src="{{ job.logo }}" alt="{{ job.company }}" class="w-12 h-12 rounded-lg object-cover shrink-0" loading="lazy" onerror="this.src='/favicon/android-chrome-192x192.png'">
          <div class="flex-1 min-w-0">
            <h3 class="text-lg font-semibold text-gray-900 dark:text-white mb-1">{{ job.position }}</h3>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-400 mb-2">{{ job.company }}</p>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap items-center gap-x-4 gap-y-1 text-sm text-gray-500 dark:text-gray-400 mb-3">
              <span class="flex items-center gap-1">
                <i data-lucide="map-pin" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
                {{ job.location }}
              </span>
              <span class="flex items-center gap-1">
                <i data-lucide="clock" class="w-3.5 h-3.5"></i>
                {{ job.post_date | timeAgo }}
              </span>
            </div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
              {% if job.reloc %}<span class="badge badge-reloc">{{ job.reloc }}</span>{% endif %}
              {% if job.visa %}<span class="badge badge-visa">{{ job.visa }}</span>{% endif %}
              <span class="badge badge-contract">{{ job.contract }}</span>
            </div>
          </div>
          <a href="{{ job.description }}" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="job-card-apply">
            Apply <i data-lucide="external-link" class="w-3.5 h-3.5 ml-1.5"></i>
          </a>
        </div>
      </div>
      {% endif %}
      {% endfor %}
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

{# SEO Content #}
<section class="py-12 bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900/50">
  <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-4 prose dark:prose-invert max-w-none">
    <h2 class="section-heading">Working in the Netherlands as a Tech Professional</h2>
    <p>
      The Netherlands is one of Europe's most welcoming countries for international tech talent. Amsterdam, Rotterdam, and Eindhoven host vibrant tech ecosystems with companies ranging from established multinationals to innovative startups. The country's strategic location, excellent infrastructure, and near-universal English proficiency make it a top choice for relocating professionals.
    </p>
    <p>
      The <strong>30% ruling</strong> is a major financial incentive — qualifying expats can receive 30% of their salary tax-free for up to five years. Combined with the <strong>Highly Skilled Migrant (Kennismigrant)</strong> visa program, which offers fast-track processing through recognized sponsors, the Netherlands makes immigration straightforward for tech workers. Most employers on this page are recognized sponsors.
    </p>
    <p>
      The Dutch work culture emphasizes work-life balance, with flexible hours and a strong consensus-driven approach. The cost of living in Amsterdam is higher than in other Dutch cities, but salaries in tech are competitive. Excellent public transport, cycling infrastructure, and a cosmopolitan lifestyle make the Netherlands an ideal base for exploring Europe.
    </p>
  </div>
</section>

